            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E8%80%85%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%82%A3%E4%B8%8A%E5%BE%AE%E7%AC%91%E5%9E%8B%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E7%97%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%BB%E4%B9%89%E8%80%85%E6%9C%89%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%82%A3%E4%B8%8A%E5%BE%AE%E7%AC%91%E5%9E%8B%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E7%97%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#完美主义者有可能患上微笑型抑郁症#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%9A%E4%BA%8B%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%BE%97%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E7%97%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%9A%E4%BA%8B%E8%BF%BD%E6%B1%82%E5%AE%8C%E7%BE%8E%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%BE%97%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E7%97%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#做事追求完美也可能得抑郁症#</span></a> 抑郁症是现在常见的一种心理疾病。我们往往觉得抑郁症患者会表现的情绪低落，其实表面上做事雷厉风行、事业成功的完美主义者，也有可能患上微笑型抑郁症。做事追求完美的人更容易忽略自己的感受，长期的压力会产生大量的负面情绪，最终累积成压垮骆驼的一根根“稻草”。<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4883557269831845" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网快看的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/75dda851ly1hcdez7eci6j20jv0b6wi6.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/uPYggRMFlx084aF8qAoE01041200RoDv0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679980833&amp;ssig=q0d85KeDYa&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/3d5pGDTvlx084aF6KBfG01041200q90j0E010.m