            <title><![CDATA[【#脊柱侧弯已成危害我国儿童的第三大疾病#[吃惊]】#我国超500万中小学生脊柱侧弯# 脊柱侧弯已经成为继肥胖、近视之后危害我国儿童青少年健康的第三大疾病。脊柱...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E4%BE%A7%E5%BC%AF%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E4%BE%A7%E5%BC%AF%E5%B7%B2%E6%88%90%E5%8D%B1%E5%AE%B3%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#脊柱侧弯已成危害我国儿童的第三大疾病#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E8%B6%85500%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E4%BE%A7%E5%BC%AF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E8%B6%85500%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%A6%E7%94%9F%E8%84%8A%E6%9F%B1%E4%BE%A7%E5%BC%AF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#我国超500万中小学生脊柱侧弯#</span></a> 脊柱侧弯已经成为继肥胖、近视之后危害我国儿童青少年健康的第三大疾病。脊柱侧弯的产生，一般多发于儿童和青少年期，由于青春发育期进展较快，一旦被忽视，就会影响日常生活和学习。预计目前我国中小学生发生脊柱侧弯人数已经超过500万，并且还在以每年30万左右的速度递增。 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4883478525968513" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/003z5L7fly8hcd0vh23q6j60zk0k0jv202.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/WgRN16Wklx084ajFiBuU010412013VB30E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679980833&amp;ssig=wu7cAc%2F2pW&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/IHg2xQj6lx084ajDTouI01041200zHIu0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679980833&amp;ssig=x1isIEddf3&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/naYBApXSlx084ajEkeLu01041200mVHx0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679980833&amp;ssig=qgh9IHYZUo&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4883478525968513&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
